There's also big open kitchen/dining room with everything you need and a big living room with cable TV and a classic Victorian bay window. I may be here, but if not, I'll make sure you're well taken care of.   West Oakland is an eclectic mix of urban and artists, with Victorians homes, warehouses, liquor stores, industrial complexes, and community gardens
name: Eclectic, Comfy Victorian Stay

description: Ultra-convenient location, streamlined no-nonsense setup, and full kitchen/living-room access make this guestroom an unbeatable value for a week in the Bay!
